  "accuracy_rules": [
    "Show the electronic/online publication date when available and do not present a future issue date as the date the research became available.",
    "Separate association from causation and animal/laboratory findings from human clinical evidence.",
    "Do not call a preprint peer reviewed. Apply eLife's Reviewed preprint label when appropriate.",
    "Report sample size and population; do not generalize beyond the studied population.",
    "Include at least one material limitation and avoid promising that early-stage results are an available treatment.",
    "Prefer the article itself over a news release; a release may be a companion link only.",
    "If the article cannot be read beyond an abstract, exclude it from the free-journal section."
